data.event: Letter of Intent signed for the purchase of a new aircraft.
Engine selection finalized and announced.

event.title: Order placed for new aircraft - later delivered

data.event: Firm order placed with the manufacturer.
Aircraft delivered from the factory.
Financing structured as a sale and lease-back.
Primary lease agreement with Global Leasing Corp.
Secondary lease agreement with Asset Management Group.
Initial delivery of the aircraft from the manufacturer.
Active service with Global Airways.

event.title: Ferry flight/moved to new storage location

data.event: Ferry flight to maintenance facility.
Heavy maintenance check performed at Shannon Aerospace.
New livery application for lease transition.
Aircraft cleared for service with new operator.
Leased to EuroFly for regional operations.
End of lease with EuroFly.

event.title: Ferry flight/moved to new storage location

data.event: Ferry flight to conversion facility.
Most comprehensive maintenance check, including structural inspections.
Conversion to cargo configuration, including main deck cargo door installation.
Dedicated cargo operations across Asia-Pacific.
Routine maintenance and scheduled engine shop visit.
Current operator for international freight.
Aircraft purchased by investor and placed in storage.

event.title: Ferry flight/moved to new storage location

data.event: Moved to long-term storage facility.
In storage.
Aircraft retired from service.
